<P>

<FONT SIZE=+2><B>MiniMed</B></FONT> is the leading supplier of insulin pumps for people with
diabetes. If you haven't been introduced to insulin pumps, and want a quick run down
on what they are and how they work, check out: <A HREF="files/how.htm"><B>"What Is An Insulin Pump and How Does It Work?"</B></A>.
<P>
For a more comprehensive overview of pump therapy, OR if you have diabetes
and want to know if it's the thing for you, check out: <A HREF="menus/is_right.htm"><B>"Is an Insulin Pump Right for You?"</B></A>.
<P>
If you're familiar with pumps and MiniMed already, and want to cut right to the chase and check out MiniMed's most advanced external insulin pump, go to: <A HREF="files/mmn078.htm"><B>The MiniMed 507</B></A>.

<P>
Whether you're a pump "newbie" or a long time user, you'll find lots of product information and pumping tips on MiniMed Web. We try to keep MiniMed Web current, so stop by every now and again and check out <A HREF="menus/whats_nu.htm"><B>What's New</B></A>. 
<P>
Send us an email; we love getting your <A HREF="files/feedbak1.htm"><B>FeedBack</B></A>.
